This is a great course. However, one thing that may trip you up is that you have to register the App which will give you an API key and then edit this line: 

admin.initializeApp(firebaseConfig);

then add: 
var firebaseConfig = {
  apiKey: "**********************",
  authDomain: "**********************",
  databaseURL: "********************",
  projectId: ***************",
  storageBucket: "******************",
  messagingSenderId: "***********************",
  appId: "**************************"
};

The above is supplied once you register the app. Otherwise, you may spend hours trying to figure out why the server keeps returning a 500 with "The incoming JSON object does not contain a client_email field."  The course does not mention this part and it WILL trip you up.

